Package: rapt
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to the APT Package Manager
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2015-02-20
Author: Dirk Eddelbuettel
Maintainer: Dirk Eddelbuettel <edd@debian.org>
Description: The APT Package Management System provides Debian and
 Debian-derived Linux systems with a powerful system to resolve package
 dependencies. This package offers access directly from R.
SystemRequirements: A Linux system using APT such as Debian, Ubuntu, or a
 suitable derivative. The 'libapt-pkg-dev' package has to be installed to
 build this package from source.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: A Debian-based system with the libapt-pkg-dev package
OS_type: unix
